&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2O
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
 CHARGE +1
 LSD
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       100
 EPS_DEFAULT  1.0E-8
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        RESTART
